As a user, I'd like to be able to move events from one existing calendar to another existing calendar. 

In this case, the current calendar owner is leaving the company.  Because we can't change the owner of the calendar itself to a different user, we'd like to move the events to a different calendar, and we can't do that either!  

The only option we see is a pain:  Recreate the calendar from scratch.

